WEBVTT

1
00:00:18.180 --> 00:00:21.400
You look beautiful today.

2
00:00:24.780 --> 00:00:25.700
Thank you.

3
00:00:29.260 --> 00:00:30.320
Are you ready?

4
00:00:30.780 --> 00:00:31.540
Before the wedding,

5
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:32.600
I want to introduce you to someone.

6
00:00:39.860 --> 00:00:42.540
I'm looking for you right now.

7
00:00:43.540 --> 00:00:48.200
I'll pick you up in half an hour.

8
00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:53.680
Lena, you're here.

9
00:00:54.580 --> 00:00:55.860
That friend you mentioned,

10
00:00:56.020 --> 00:00:56.700
what's his name?

11
00:00:56.860 --> 00:00:57.860
Where is he now?

12
00:00:58.000 --> 00:00:59.460
The gentleman saw a woman in makeup

13
00:00:59.460 --> 00:01:01.400
and wasn't upset.

14
00:01:01.680 --> 00:01:02.760
He even said she was beautiful.

15
00:01:03.260 --> 00:01:04.640
Sir, is it that you dislike

16
00:01:04.640 --> 00:01:05.320
women wearing makeup?

17
00:01:05.500 --> 00:01:05.860
Why?

18
00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:07.720
Lingling,

19
00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:09.140
then don't blame me.

